title: I vampiri
actors: Musidora, Édouard Mathé, Marcel Lévesque, Jean Aymé, Fernand Herrmann, Stacia Napierkowska, Renée Carl, Suzanne Delvé, Georgette Faraboni, Jacques Feyder, Fridolin, Rita Herlor, Émile Keppens, Louise Lagrange, Suzanne Le Bret
description: An intrepid reporter and his loyal friend battle a bizarre secret society of criminals known as The Vampires.
